This song is about us as human in comparison to prophet SA 
But also it can also be possible that prophet would have reached to this position by having similar thoughts comparing him self to his lord Allah

But in spirituality it is about the beauty of Allah in comparison to his heaven  here after and early beauty which means God is sweeter then all heavens and earthly gifts.
